[30;1m1815 | [0m[35m        defaults to quicksort. However, currently Snowpark pandas does not support quicksort;[0m
[30;1m1816 | [0m[35m        instead, stable sort is performed. Therefore, the order of the indexer returned by[0m
[30;1m1817 | [0m[35m        `Index.sort_values` is not guaranteed to match pandas' result indexer.[0m
[30;1m1818 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m1819 | [0m[35m        Examples[0m

[30;1m3850 | [0m[35m            value at a time and concatenating all resulting frames. The resulting columns[0m

[30;1m3852 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m3853 | [0m[35m            Snowpark pandas does not currently support sequences of int for `periods`.[0m
